Package: superheroR
Title: Superhero API Wrapper
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Edgar",
           family = "Zamora",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "edgarzamora2012@hotmail.com")
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: A R wrapper that can be used to pull data from the SuperHero API <https://superheroapi.com> by specific superhero.
    Entering the desired superhero you can information regarding a superheros powerstats, appearances, connections, and
    much more. A Facebook profile is required to obtain a token.
